Package: Friedman
Title: Simple Visualization Wrappers for Exploratory Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Animesh", "Singh", email = "animesh664@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small set of wrapper functions around ggplot2 and lattice
    for quickly making common plots like histograms, scatter plots, and
    box plots during exploratory data analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: ggplot2, lattice, rlang, stats
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/Meshqc/Friedman
BugReports: https://github.com/Meshqc/Friedman/issues
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
